ource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/76faca0ac0a59498daf76285f9bda91f.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/76faca0ac0a59498daf76285f9bda91f.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Finish with style.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.poster.avif?t=1704981119\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.webm?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287100/extras/9f98d48b8fae03866828908779d9b201.mp4?t=1704981119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Original mechanics</strong>. Move through the lines and find the correct path to kill all enemies.<br></li><li><strong>40+ hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing complexity.<br></li><li><strong>Beautiful environments</strong> of Japan in the feudal era.<br></li><li><strong>Easy controls</strong>. Only mouse clicks.</li></ul>",
